quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  33,23,"Kubva muvatendi mune varume vaiva pachokwadi muzvitsidzo zvavo naAllah (vakatsungirira kurwa munzira yaAllah). Mavari mune vamwe vakazadzisa zvirevo zvavo (vakauraiwa kuhondo), uye vamwe vachakangomirira, asi havana kumbobvira vashandura (chitsidzirano chavo naAllah) kana zvishoma"
  33,24,"Kuti Allah vave vanoripa varume vechokwadi nekuda kwechokwadi chavo, uyezve vorwadzisa vanyengedzi kana vachida kana kutambira ruregerero rwavo (vachiratidza tsitsi dzavo). Zvirokwazvo, Allah vanoregerera zvikuru, vane nyasha zhinji"
  33,25,Uye Allah vakadzorera mumashure avo vanhu vasingatendi vakatsamwa. Havana kana chitsvene chavakawana. Allah vakabatsira vatendi mukurwa (nekutumira mhepo nengirozi). Uye Allah ndivo samasimba vane masimba
  33,26,"Uye avo vanhu vegwaro vakave vanobatsira (vasingatendi), Allah vakavadzikisa kubva munzvimbo dzavo uye vakave vanoisa kutya muhana dzavo, kusvikira chimwe chikwata chavo makauraya uye chimwe mukachisunga"
  33,27,"Uye vakaita kuti mutore minda yavo, uye dzimba dzavo, neupfumi hwavo, uye zvekare iyo nzvimbo yamange musati mambotsika (mumashure). Uye Allah vane masimba pamusoro pezvinhu zvose"
  33,28,"Iwe muporofita (Muhammad SAW))! Taurira madzimai ako kuti: “Kana muchida hupenyu hwepano pasi pamwe nezvinofadza zvavo (hupenyu), kuti huyai ndikugadzirirei zvitsvene pamwe nekukusunungurai mune zvakanaka (kukurambai).”"
  33,29,"“Asi kana muchida Allah pamwe nemutumwa wavo (SAW), uye nemisha yamangwana, zvirokwazvo Allah vakagadzirira madzimai vanoita mabasa akanaka kubva kwamuri mubairo mukuru.”"
  33,30,"Imi madzimai amuporofita! Uyo kubva kwamuri anenge aita chitadzo chinooneka (Faahishah: Chitadzo chikuru kana hupombwe), mutongo wamarwadzo kwaari unenge uri pauviri, uye zvinhu zvidukusa kuna Allah"